  "storyboard_markdown": "# Scene Contract: CH001_SC003\n\n## Production Intent\nEstablish the physical threat of the Apache presence through a transition from quiet observation to high-intensity combat. The sequence must move from controlled, observational shots in the valley to chaotic, handheld movement during the skirmish on the plateau.\n\n## Required Cast\n- john_carter (Rugged survivor/Confederate cavalry attire)\n- apache_warriors (Large group)\n\n## Required Environments\n- Arizona hills/valley (with quartz vein)\n- Narrow cliffside trail\n- High plateau camp\n\n## Continuity Constraints\n- Total count of apache_warriors must remain consistent during skirmish.\n- Direction of pursuit: Valley -> Trail -> Plateau.\n- Weapon handling: Consistent use of rifles and sidearms for carter and warriors.\n\n## Beat List\n- BT001: Detection of movement in the valley.\n- BT002: Pursuit along the narrow cliffside trail.\n- BT003: Discovery of camp and chaotic skirmish eruption.",
